It's 10 yuan.

00:35:11.070 --> 00:35:11.670
Drink up!

00:35:12.780 --> 00:35:13.580
Cheers!

00:35:25.840 --> 00:35:27.100
What's wrong with you?

00:35:28.250 --> 00:35:30.960
[Guo Yaoyang, A Henchman of He Gang's]

00:35:31.710 --> 00:35:33.190
-I said, "Let me through."
-What are you doing?

00:35:33.190 --> 00:35:34.320
Harassing a lady, aren't you?

00:35:34.320 --> 00:35:35.150
I'll call the police!

00:35:35.150 --> 00:35:35.950
What the heck?

00:35:36.110 --> 00:35:36.980
What's wrong with you?

00:35:36.980 --> 00:35:38.180
Are you crazy or what?

00:35:43.480 --> 00:35:44.630
How could you assault people?

00:35:44.630 --> 00:35:45.800
Look what you've done to my place!

00:35:45.800 --> 00:35:46.280
Let go of me.

00:35:46.280 --> 00:35:47.150
What are you trying to do?

00:35:47.150 --> 00:35:48.030
Let go of me!

00:35:54.960 --> 00:35:55.960
Listen up,

00:35:57.150 --> 00:35:58.410
my name is Guo Yaoyang.

00:35:59.280 --> 00:35:59.320
From now on,

00:35:59.320 --> 00:36:00.510
[Seafood Barbecue]

00:36:00.510 --> 00:36:01.960
when you do business here,

00:36:01.960 --> 00:36:03.090
remember to behave!

00:36:07.840 --> 00:36:08.940
Are you okay, sir?

00:36:09.840 --> 00:36:10.700
Unacceptable.

00:36:11.920 --> 00:36:13.110
I must call the police.

00:36:13.110 --> 00:36:14.110
Let it slide, sir.

00:36:14.760 --> 00:36:16.670
Mr. Guo works for He Gang.

00:36:16.840 --> 00:36:18.040
Just drop the matter.

00:36:18.510 --> 00:36:19.070
Come on.

00:36:19.590 --> 00:36:20.110
Get up.

00:36:21.280 --> 00:36:22.760
If anyone dares to disrespect you,

00:36:22.760 --> 00:36:25.320
just declare
that you're Guo Yaoyang's girlfriend.

00:36:25.320 --> 00:36:25.960
Got it.

00:36:25.960 --> 00:36:28.020
Then I'll beat that person up for you.

00:36:28.920 --> 00:36:30.070
I need to use the bathroom. Wait for me.

00:36:30.070 --> 00:36:30.630
Sure.

00:36:30.960 --> 00:36:31.710
You two coming with me?

00:36:31.710 --> 00:36:32.280
Yes.

00:36:33.110 --> 00:36:35.040
Let's see who can pee the farthest.

00:36:36.230 --> 00:36:38.200
I bet you two are going to lose.

00:37:01.000 --> 00:37:02.440
Dude, what do you mean by this?

00:37:02.440 --> 00:37:03.230
Tell me.

00:37:03.800 --> 00:37:04.800
What's your name?

00:37:07.440 --> 00:37:08.170
Guo Yaoyang.

00:37:08.480 --> 00:37:09.080
What's up?

00:37:09.440 --> 00:37:10.640
You're quite famous.

00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:14.530
Please, sir.

00:37:14.710 --> 00:37:15.710
I have a question.

00:37:16.280 --> 00:37:16.840
Yes, sir?

00:37:17.960 --> 00:37:19.280
Are those gambling dens there

00:37:19.280 --> 00:37:20.190
all yours?

00:37:20.660 --> 00:37:21.520
Gambling dens?

00:37:22.070 --> 00:37:24.200
I don't know, sir. I'm not a local here.

00:37:30.900 --> 00:37:31.670
Sir,

00:37:35.150 --> 00:37:36.030
I recall it now.

00:37:36.190 --> 00:37:36.920
I recall it.

00:37:37.550 --> 00:37:38.350
They're mine.

00:37:39.280 --> 00:37:40.810
Are you running them alone?

00:37:40.960 --> 00:37:42.190
Yes, all by myself.

00:37:46.110 --> 00:37:46.630
Sir...

00:37:47.920 --> 00:37:49.120
I'm not finished yet.

00:37:50.760 --> 00:37:52.020
They belong to He Gang.

00:37:52.800 --> 00:37:54.530
I'm just watching them for him.

00:37:54.670 --> 00:37:56.200
The dens belong to him only?

00:37:56.360 --> 00:37:57.000
No.

00:37:57.840 --> 00:37:59.970
They belong to his brother He Biao too,

00:38:00.590 --> 00:38:02.190
who owns the Grand Paradise.

00:38:05.230 --> 00:38:06.030
Sir, sir, sir,

00:38:06.230 --> 00:38:07.000
this is all I know.

00:38:07.000 --> 00:38:07.510
I...

00:38:07.880 --> 00:38:09.340
I've told you everything.

00:38:09.360 --> 00:38:10.690
Do you know who Ma Jin is?

00:38:10.840 --> 00:38:11.550
Mr. Ma?

00:38:12.550 --> 00:38:14.750
Those gambling dens used to be Mr. Ma's,

00:38:14.840 --> 00:38:15.880
but then somehow they fell

00:38:15.880 --> 00:38:17.880
into the hands of He Biao and He Gang.

00:38:18.070 --> 00:38:19.320
This is really all I know, sir.

00:38:19.320 --> 00:38:20.590
I-I'm just

00:38:20.710 --> 00:38:21.670
a nobody.

00:38:21.670 --> 00:38:23.670
Sir, calm down.

00:38:24.110 --> 00:38:25.110
Have a cigarette.

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:26.860
Stop being mad.

00:38:28.510 --> 00:38:29.840
I'll ask around for you.

00:38:30.190 --> 00:38:31.190
Is that okay, sir?

00:38:31.510 --> 00:38:32.920
H-How should I call you, sir?

00:38:32.920 --> 00:38:33.850
What do you mean?

00:38:33.920 --> 00:38:35.580
You're asking my name, right?

00:38:36.000 --> 00:38:37.600
I'll just ask around for you.

00:38:38.150 --> 00:38:39.280
I mean nothing else.

00:38:41.110 --> 00:38:42.760
What's going on with these two?

00:38:42.760 --> 00:38:44.630
I hit them each once,
and now they're like this?

00:38:44.630 --> 00:38:45.960
Both of you, get up! Hurry!

00:38:45.960 --> 00:38:48.280
Nothing serious.
I'm bleeding but still fine.

00:38:48.280 --> 00:38:48.840
Get up!

00:38:49.960 --> 00:38:50.710
Can you walk?

00:38:50.710 --> 00:38:51.310
Yes, I can.

00:38:51.400 --> 00:38:51.880
Are you sure?

00:38:51.880 --> 00:38:53.010
I'm perfectly fine.

00:38:53.280 --> 00:38:53.880
Good.

00:38:55.550 --> 00:38:57.150
I'll come to you if I need anything.

00:38:57.150 --> 00:38:57.880
Sure, sir.

00:39:05.510 --> 00:39:06.630
Take care, sir!

00:39:10.360 --> 00:39:11.220
Here, Hongbao.

00:39:12.550 --> 00:39:14.040
Oh, Mr. Bao!

00:39:14.110 --> 00:39:14.760
Mr. Bao!

00:39:14.760 --> 00:39:16.560
What happened to you?

00:39:17.190 --> 00:39:18.500
Si, tidy up the place.

00:39:18.880 --> 00:39:20.080
Give me some tissues.

00:39:20.840 --> 00:39:21.630
Mr. Bao,

00:39:21.630 --> 00:39:22.760
it's me, Jiu.

00:39:22.960 --> 00:39:24.140
Si is back!

00:39:24.670 --> 00:39:25.400
Look.

00:39:25.550 --> 00:39:26.880
Look who's back.

00:39:27.330 --> 00:39:29.130
[Mr. Bao, Su Hongbao's Boss]

00:39:31.880 --> 00:39:32.790
You've recognized him.

00:39:32.790 --> 00:39:33.720
You really have.

00:39:39.280 --> 00:39:40.190
Wasn't it just a fall?

00:39:40.190 --> 00:39:40.760
How did he

00:39:41.030 --> 00:39:41.960
end up like this?

00:39:43.070 --> 00:39:44.630
It was all because of Ma Jin.

00:39:44.960 --> 00:39:46.440
Mr. Bao had a cerebral hemorrhage

00:39:46.440 --> 00:39:47.630
and nearly died.

00:39:47.800 --> 00:39:49.150
Our brothers all chipped in to help him.

00:39:49.150 --> 00:39:50.600
That was how he survived.

00:39:50.760 --> 00:39:52.090
We're still in debt now.

00:40:12.590 --> 00:40:13.760
Mr. Bao, I'm back.

00:40:16.230 --> 00:40:17.320
Don't worry.

00:40:18.840 --> 00:40:19.840
I will get back

00:40:20.510 --> 00:40:21.760
what should be ours.

00:40:23.550 --> 00:40:25.550
Then I'll get you proper treatment.

00:40:26.070 --> 00:40:26.420
Hongbao,

00:40:26.420 --> 00:40:27.070
[Wu Si, A Henchman of Su Hongbao's]

00:40:27.070 --> 00:40:28.570
I waited so long for you to say that.

00:40:28.570 --> 00:40:30.150
After suffering for so many years,

00:40:30.150 --> 00:40:31.760
I can't take it anymore.

00:40:32.630 --> 00:40:35.360
We must make a big move
before we get too old for it.

00:40:36.710 --> 00:40:37.280
Jiu!

00:40:37.710 --> 00:40:38.630
Close that restaurant of yours.

00:40:38.630 --> 00:40:39.710
Let's all work together.

00:40:39.710 --> 00:40:40.320
Si,

00:40:41.440 --> 00:40:43.330
things are difficult for me.

00:40:48.440 --> 00:40:49.030
Hongbao,

00:40:50.550 --> 00:40:51.670
truth to be told,

00:40:51.670 --> 00:40:53.510
I'm in poor health now.

00:40:54.030 --> 00:40:56.360
I just want to keep running my restaurant,

00:40:56.510 --> 00:40:57.480
make a living,

00:40:58.000 --> 00:40:59.280
and live a stable life.

00:41:01.440 --> 00:41:02.210
It's okay.

00:41:03.250 --> 00:41:05.110
People pursue different things.

00:41:06.540 --> 00:41:07.760
Go buy Mr. Bao

00:41:07.760 --> 00:41:08.870
some fruit then.

00:41:09.190 --> 00:41:09.880
Hongbao, there's money on me.

00:41:09.880 --> 00:41:11.140
I'll go buy some fruit.

00:41:14.110 --> 00:41:15.030
What a coward.

00:41:15.440 --> 00:41:17.840
Jiu was cowardly before,
and now he's even more so.

00:41:17.840 --> 00:41:18.370
Hongbao,

00:41:18.480 --> 00:41:21.080
the two of us can make a proper team
without him.

00:41:21.960 --> 00:41:23.510
Mr. Bao, easy, easy.

00:41:23.630 --> 00:41:24.840
This is Hongbao.

00:41:24.840 --> 00:41:25.590
Si.

00:41:27.990 --> 00:41:29.680
Look into

00:41:30.150 --> 00:41:31.590
He Biao and He Gang.

00:41:32.960 --> 00:41:33.840
Figure out their backgrounds.

00:41:33.840 --> 00:41:35.640
I think someone's backing them.

00:41:36.590 --> 00:41:37.510
By the way,

00:41:38.960 --> 00:41:39.880
Lin didn't die.

00:41:43.320 --> 00:41:44.400
Lin didn't die.

00:41:47.070 --> 00:41:48.200
Think of something.

00:41:48.800 --> 00:41:49.630
Try...

00:41:50.840 --> 00:41:52.880
if you can get his contact.

00:41:56.630 --> 00:41:57.360
Qin,

00:41:57.710 --> 00:41:58.420
something came up.

00:41:58.420 --> 00:41:59.550
Okay. What is it?

00:42:00.280 --> 00:42:01.400
Didn't you ask me to keep

00:42:01.400 --> 00:42:03.000
close watch on Lin's home,

00:42:03.000 --> 00:42:04.200
who worked for Ma Jin?

00:42:04.670 --> 00:42:06.280
All was quiet until a few days ago,

00:42:06.280 --> 00:42:08.000
someone came find him.

00:42:08.230 --> 00:42:08.840
Who was it?

00:42:08.960 --> 00:42:11.000
A man named Su Hongbao. I looked into him.

00:42:11.000 --> 00:42:13.260
He's an ex-con who just got out of prison.

00:42:13.280 --> 00:42:14.960
Do you need me to dig deeper?

00:42:15.920 --> 00:42:17.110
I know this guy.

00:42:17.960 --> 00:42:18.960
You know him?

00:42:21.150 --> 00:42:22.550
It was I who arrested him.

00:42:23.320 --> 00:42:23.920
It's okay.

00:42:25.170 --> 00:42:26.130
Leave this to me.

00:42:26.360 --> 00:42:27.820
He's not your problem now.

00:42:28.710 --> 00:42:29.240
Alright.

00:42:36.190 --> 00:42:39.660
[In loving memory
of my beloved daughter Qian Yuhong]

00:42:40.780 --> 00:42:41.880
Yuhong,

00:42:43.880 --> 00:42:46.480
how time flies.

00:42:47.510 --> 00:42:48.710
In the blink of an eye,

00:42:49.800 --> 00:42:51.400
we've been apart for 2 years.

00:42:53.150 --> 00:42:55.210
In dreams I forget I'm just a visitor,

00:42:55.800 --> 00:42:58.130
yet waking feels like I'm still dreaming.

