Secretly running gambling dens
behind our backs?

00:43:15.780 --> 00:43:17.710
Is it because I, He Muzhi, have been

00:43:17.730 --> 00:43:19.640
appearing too refined in public lately?

00:43:19.640 --> 00:43:20.640
Yeah.

00:43:22.110 --> 00:43:23.420
But it's a bit tricky

00:43:24.840 --> 00:43:26.240
to deal with this person.

00:43:26.360 --> 00:43:27.600
It's Liu Tianfei.

00:43:27.970 --> 00:43:28.570
Muzhi,

00:43:28.890 --> 00:43:30.270
your tactics to manage people
aren't working well.

